  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 29: Bergstraße Express – North to Otzberg</name>
    <desc>A long northern arc combining the Bergstraße, two impressive castles—Veste Otzberg and Burg Breuberg—and the scenic Odenwald heartland. An ambitious day exploring the northern reaches of the riding area.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
